{"tid":2046692,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"人際戰術","createTime":"2020-06-01T14:43:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-09T21:25:34.000Z","uid":47901,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"59edeabe427cb406882cecdf81232c68de44ce60","tid":2046692,"uid":47901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T14:43:44.000Z","msg":"有冇發覺時下港女好中意話人地&ldquo;搞笑&rdquo;以表示自己的不滿，或對不公義的批評?  佢地好似幾乎冇其他形容詞<br />\n<br />\n或者，有冇發覺在討論的場合上，人多數以話對&ldquo;on9&rdquo;去表達自己的反對?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我是想談一談香港人際間的戰術，同人際戰鬥上一d有關成本效益，出牌相克的問題，我希望可以對多年的觀察作一個戰術概括"},{"pid":"9248266d4445eb774688d1fe6b999bcd40569b36","tid":2046692,"uid":47901,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T14:50:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/9fUyul2Hg18\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F9fUyul2Hg18&d=f5Yas2EExEus6787o4Ns8%2BdFAmKeyJhstBKVrdqrVyA%3D&h=ddc9cb15\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/9fUyul2Hg18</a>"},{"pid":"c012cbcd483f3148d1f7cd6a7f2f373f32fca8e4","tid":2046692,"uid":310015,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T18:33:10.000Z","msg":"Lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf5c212ac9312eee6d574154010a66aee8c08386","tid":2046692,"uid":47901,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"c012cbcd483f3148d1f7cd6a7f2f373f32fca8e4","tid":2046692,"uid":310015,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T18:33:10.000Z","msg":"Lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T22:47:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e60a4d01ae779dffdb0a61862a8e1b663396ede3","tid":2046692,"uid":99930,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T22:56:10.000Z","msg":"打超限戰必勝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"920d5bb33885a59e2b2fc36d7d9c91a2cf8c0997","tid":2046692,"uid":47901,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"e60a4d01ae779dffdb0a61862a8e1b663396ede3","tid":2046692,"uid":99930,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T22:56:10.000Z","msg":"打超限戰必勝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T23:33:26.000Z","msg":"超限戰!"},{"pid":"ba91cd8b9b6be3a462e7dc6047600682128e8ffa","tid":2046692,"uid":47901,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"59edeabe427cb406882cecdf81232c68de44ce60","tid":2046692,"uid":47901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T14:43:44.000Z","msg":"有冇發覺時下港女好中意話人地&ldquo;搞笑&rdquo;以表示自己的不滿，或對不公義的批評?  佢地好似幾乎冇其他形容詞<br />\n<br />\n或者，有冇發覺在討論的場合上，人多數以話對&ldquo;on9&rdquo;去表達自己的反對?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我是想談一談香港人際間的戰術，同人際戰鬥上一d有關成本效益，出牌相克的問題，我希望可以對多年的觀察作一個戰術概括"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T01:33:11.000Z","msg":"無論一個人如何臭串，如果無禮至極，如何&ldquo;蔑視&rdquo;，如何兇惡，如何&ldquo;陰險&rdquo;，如何&ldquo;背信棄義&quot;，如何&ldquo;殘忍&rdquo;，如何&ldquo;負心&rdquo;，如何&ldquo;不公義&rdquo;，如何&ldquo;無情&rdquo;，如何&ldquo;薄情&rdquo;，如何&ldquo;小器&rdquo;，如何&quot;計較&quot;........<br />\n<br />\n那些港女，或討論區上的人，絕少見批評那個人以直接同符合的形容詞<br />\n<br />\n基本上全部統稱&ldquo;on9&rdquo;, &quot;搞笑&quot;，&ldquo;弱智&rdquo;，有時以&ldquo;痴根&rdquo;，&ldquo;白卡&rdquo; ， 諸如此類<br />\n<br />\n他們不是無讀書，不是不識字，可能考試測驗有豐富詞彙，<br />\n<br />\n但他們絕少會用的， 為何?<br />\n<br />\n我諗，其實係一個，由經歷長久人際戰鬥經驗而促成的&quot;有效常規出牌策略&quot;"},{"pid":"68b4a8d063f9d0ccf233c316e546d945ebb807c8","tid":2046692,"uid":47901,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T00:08:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/2CGpK7ZgqIQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F2CGpK7ZgqIQ&d=f5Yas2EExEu